reviews.content:
Wow wow wow it exceeded my hopes as a beautiful, creative, open ended play for my toddler that was NOT loud, overstimulating, or chaotic. I mean I literally felt so calm and relaxed, as I sipped coffee and enjoyed watching my little one explore the many options for gross and fine motor play, sensory play, music and games. We will 100% be signing him up for the science and music classes. Ashley was a responsive and generous host to the group of littles.

Music for grownups without lyrics and a classical version playing; very comfortable seating options for us, where you can easily keep an eye on your kid, they prioritize safety and cleanliness. The toys and activities for kids are top of the line, amazing quality, and spark joy and creativity ❤️

Thanks for a great first visit, we will be back soon with more friends!}
